Package graph.properties

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bipartite<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
    A class for checking the bipartite property of a graph Bipartite graph (or bigraph) is a graph whose vertices can be divided into two disjoint sets U and V (that is, U and V are each independent sets) such that every edge connects a vertex in U to one in V.
    GraphProperties<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
    A class containing methods for checking various properties of the given graph
